<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="mb-4">About CharityConnect</h1>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>CharityConnect aims to bridge the gap between donors and charities by providing a platform that facilitates efficient and targeted donations. We believe that by connecting those who want to give with those who need help, we can make a significant positive impact on our communities.</p>
                    
                    <p>Our platform enables charities to specify exactly what items they need, and allows donors to contribute those specific items, ensuring that donations are always useful and relevant.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">How It Works</h2>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                            <div class="rounded-circle bg-primary text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h5>Charities Register</h5>
                            <p class="small text-muted">Charities create profiles and get verified by our admin team.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                            <div class="rounded-circle bg-primary text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-list-alt"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h5>Post Requests</h5>
                            <p class="small text-muted">Charities post specific requests for items they need.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                            <div class="rounded-circle bg-primary text-white d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                                <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h5>Donors Contribute</h5>
                            <p class="small text-muted">Donors browse and fulfill requests that match their giving goals.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Our Values</h2>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Transparency:</strong> We believe in complete transparency in the donation process, ensuring donors know exactly where their contributions are going.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Efficiency:</strong> Our platform is designed to minimize waste and ensure that donations meet real needs.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Community:</strong> We foster a sense of community by connecting local donors with local charities.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Accessibility:</strong> We strive to make giving as easy and accessible as possible for everyone.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Impact:</strong> We focus on maximizing the impact of every donation by ensuring it meets a specific need.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3">Join Us</h2>
                    <p>Whether you're a charity in need of donations or a donor looking to make a difference, CharityConnect provides the platform to connect and contribute effectively.</p>
                    
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-4">
                        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Contact Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
